data.title: Michael Dell
data.meta_description: Michael Dell - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Michael Dell is an American businessman who founded Dell Inc. and is its CEO. He was born in 1965 in Houston, Texas and became interested in computers at a young age. Dell started upgrading computers as a student at University of Texas to earn extra money, which led him to found Dell Computer Corporation in 1984. Dell grew his company rapidly to become the largest personal computer manufacturer in the world. He has a net worth of over $14 billion and received numerous business awards for his success in revolutionizing the PC industry.
